title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 §§ 646-1.7 - Exemptions
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 §§ 646-1.7 - Exemptions

State Regulations

The permit application requirements of this Subpart shall
not be applicable to the State, including agencies of the State, or any
municipality acting in a governmental capacity. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6
§§
646-1.7

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
